name: Hinata / Hinata Hyūga (日向 ヒナタ) / [Naruto: Shippuden]
description:
This Lora was a tricky one to make since she has a large dataset and that why choosing the right images took a lot of time. After searching through every inch of the internet, i dense it down to 183 images. Trained on 768x768 reso. Use weight between 0.7 ~ 0.8 .
I don't think this model is perfect by any chance but it a decent one.
If you like the model please consider leaving a review.

Trained for 4 epoches but the forth one is overfit so decided to publish the 3rd Epoch.

I was going to fix the issues but since i'm too lazy to do it here are the known issues :

  • Her hoodie can be whacky sometime especially clothes manipulation such as windy effect or open clothes etc.

  • Her blue pants is not recognized very well resulting in blue jeans pants. (probably need more training for the lower half)

  • Can't produce fishnets really well. At least it's acceptable. So, Good Luck trying.

  • On her alternate hairstyle(side ponytail),can appear on both side. If that happen Keep generating. you'll eventually get the right one or the left XD.

This Lora Include 2 versions the Original Shippuden Outfit and the Alternate Hairstyle from the onsen Scene. Both versions can be used interchangeably.

Basic Prompt for Shippuden Outfit:
masterpiece, absurdres, 1girl, hinata\(shippuden\),solo,blush, hooded jacket, headband around neck, konohagakure symbol, fishnets, blue pants, looking at viewer, outdoors, sunlight,smile,cowboy shot

Basic Prompt for alternate Hairstyle:
masterpiece, absurdres, 1girl, hinata\(shippuden\), solo, naked towel, large breasts, grabbing own breast, alternate hairstyle, side ponytail, looking at viewer, blush, embarrassed,

If you want to replicate the sample images here is the model that i used : anything-v4.5.safetensors
